佬係隔離鳩叫<br />\n<br />\n收手啦公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪想比人笑到面黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"你平行時空...?<br />\n公屋仔間屋大撚過我地私樓仔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0752158313c5b833b58767bdbf6a673b6454ed90","tid":1015491,"uid":22148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8383b2c012c9eba37257279f5caf180dd7fe6e","tid":1015491,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab21d935e0a7e7a79fcd6d566d68fc3f3d5eaef2","tid":1015491,"uid":22148,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"7c8a1d0c72f36d6dd470bc68038c70770e5f3c29","tid":1015491,"uid":105366,"like":10,"dislike":21,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"結婚十八年<br />\n公屋仔大，老婆係私樓妹。<br />\n有乜問題？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"唔係你老婆肯嫁你，你仲係公屋仔..<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"下，我都係公屋仔，老婆小富之家<br />\n我毫子無洗過外家，結婚六十萬都係自己出，依家咪又係有屋揸手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登佬，你不如代入樓主呀..<br />\n我好憎d人成日都話「我以前咪又係捱」..<br />\nD口氣同d廢老有乜分別？<br />\n我唔係話你唔叻..<br />\n<br />\n但樓主今年可能20頭剛做嘢.. 佢想表達果隻「無力感」..<br />\n如果樓主早10年出世，而家都可能有樓揸手.. <br />\n但唔代表「而家」個社會嘅公屋私樓論不是問題..<br />\n<br />\n我都有樓，但我唔覺得應該有樓去量度..<br />\n早幾年買樓結婚，知道自己屋企無能support，老婆住居樓但有樓收租。<br />\n<br />\n自己心內忐忑不定，一方面覺得「竹門對竹門」，另一方面又會好無力，無人幫，最後都係頂住頭皮.. 唔通我而家反轉頭指住班後生仔，話佢哋無用咩..."},{"pid":"e03d7fc2e9a69e92fc288dfb29ead1ce183e0aac","tid":1015491,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08921783bfc7d9d3c9e5d56e1f4008c615b22fc2","tid":1015491,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b88b08ecf7bf448fe952383c994d0c07d4d96dd8","tid":1015491,"uid":22148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b26325e267ca12c74daa396e664627ae56de683","tid":1015491,"uid":105366,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"哈，你點assume我係2000年買樓呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1) 我唔喺凸區， 2)我2016年先買屋，之前一直租。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"我11先出黎做嘢，未有經濟能力，儲到16年先夠首期.. 你咁早出黎做嘢，食正條水都要等到2016.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:16:21.000Z","msg":"因為我喺美國，之前租唔貴。我地冇細路，亦唔諗住生。所以一直冇買。首期一早有。到2016先決定買因為租金開始因呢度樓市而發顛而貴過供樓先決定買。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"咁你唔好返香港！<br />\n香港真係有錢有生活..."},{"pid":"072168f1c71d9b1e009483aedc6964d2c5f41422","tid":1015491,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b46aa9799ac0ee13db1307ff905f23d6f29f588","tid":1015491,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"有學歷另計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸 私樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"點為之有學歷？有學歷大把人！"},{"pid":"cfc7ba9a8d4857280634bea4556fa4581704ba25","tid":1015491,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0752158313c5b833b58767bdbf6a673b6454ed90","tid":1015491,"uid":22148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8